p; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">增强的频率组系统，每组最多</span><span lang="EN-US">12</span><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个兼容频率</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">高品质的纯分集接收技术</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">导音静噪技术可以在发射机关闭时去除无线射频干扰</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">自动频率扫描功能可以自动寻找可用频率</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">增强的音频频率范围</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">利用红外线界面与无线发射机同频</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">具有更多可控选项的用户友好的菜单操作</span><span lang="EN-US"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times Ne